    "General-purpose feature descriptors that have been applied for plankton images include Histogram of Oriented Gradient (HOG) (Dalal and Triggs 2005; Bi et al. 2015; Guo et al. 2021c), Scale Invariant Feature Transform (SIFT) (Lowe 2004; Tsechpenakis et al. 2007), Speeded Up Robust Features (SURF) (Bay et al. 2006; Chang et al. 2016), Inner-Distance shape context (IDSC) (Ling and Jacobs 2007; Zheng et al. 2017), and Phase congruency descriptors (PCD) (Kovesi 2000; Sánchez et al. 2019b; Verikas et al. 2012).",
